          "4. Spread the ground beef over the chips and sprinkle with grated cheese.",
          "5. Bake in the oven at 200°C (400°F) for 8-10 minutes until the cheese has melted.",
          "6. Top with guacamole, sour cream and jalapeño slices before serving."
